<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>AI Industrial Filtration Decision Engine | UNITE FILTER</title>

<style>
body {
  margin:0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background:#0b1220;
  color:#ffffff;
}

.container {
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:60px 20px;
}

.hero {
  text-align:center;
  padding:80px 20px;
}

h1 {
  font-size:42px;
  line-height:1.2;
}

.highlight {
  color:#4da3ff;
}

.sub {
  color:#b6c2d1;
  font-size:18px;
  margin-top:15px;
}

.cta {
  margin-top:30px;
}

button {
  padding:12px 20px;
  margin:10px;
  border:none;
  cursor:pointer;
  border-radius:6px;
  font-size:14px;
}

.primary {
  background:#4da3ff;
  color:white;
}

.secondary {
  background:transparent;
  border:1px solid #4da3ff;
  color:#4da3ff;
}

.section {
  margin-top:80px;
}

.card {
  background:#111a2e;
  padding:20px;
  border-radius:10px;
  margin-top:15px;
}

.grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:15px;
}

.tag {
  display:inline-block;
  background:#1d2a44;
  padding:6px 10px;
  margin:5px;
  border-radius:6px;
  font-size:12px;
  color:#9fb3c8;
}

table {
  width:100%;
  margin-top:20px;
  border-collapse:collapse;
}

td,th {
  border:1px solid #22314d;
  padding:10px;
  text-align:center;
}

.footer {
  text-align:center;
  margin-top:80px;
  color:#6b7c93;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <h1>
    Design Industrial Filtration Systems <span class="highlight">in Seconds</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="sub">
    AI-powered engineering decision engine for process filtration system selection.
    Replace manual experience with data-driven recommendations.
  </p>

  <div class="cta">
    <button class="primary">🚀 Try Live Tool</button>
    <button class="secondary">📄 View Example Report</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Industrial Filtration Selection is Still Manual</h2>

  <div class="card">
    Engineers still rely on catalogs, experience, and trial-and-error design.<br><br>
    This leads to:
    <ul>
      <li>Long engineering cycles</li>
      <li>High selection risk</li>
      <li>Inconsistent system design</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SOLUTION -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>We Built an AI Engineering Decision Engine</h2>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Input Layer</h3>
      <p>Flow, pressure, solid content, particle size</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>AI Engine</h3>
      <p>Engineering rules + industrial knowledge base</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Output System</h3>
      <p>Top 3 filtration system recommendations</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Key Features</h2>

  <div class="card">
    ✔ Engineering AI decision logic<br>
    ✔ Multi-parameter system matching<br>
    ✔ Industrial filtration knowledge base<br>
    ✔ Instant comparison engine<br>
    ✔ Exportable engineering reports
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SYSTEMS -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Supported Filtration Systems</h2>

  <div>
    <span class="tag">Bag Filter</span>
    <span class="tag">Cartridge Filter</span>
    <span class="tag">Backwash Filter</span>
    <span class="tag">Pressure Leaf Filter</span>
    <span class="tag">Self-cleaning Filter</span>
    <span class="tag">Coalescer</span>
    <span class="tag">Separator</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- USE CASES -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Industries</h2>

  <div class="card">
    Chemical • Petrochemical • Pharmaceutical • Food & Beverage • Energy • Water Treatment
  </div>
</div>

<!-- COMPARISON -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Example Output Comparison</h2>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Parameter</th>
      <th>Bag Filter</th>
      <th>Backwash Filter</th>
      <th>Leaf Filter</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>High Solid</td>
      <td>✔</td>
      <td>✔</td>
      <td>✔✔</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Continuous Operation</td>
      <td>✖</td>
      <td>✔✔</td>
      <td>✖</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Fine Filtration</td>
      <td>✔</td>
      <td>✔</td>
      <td>✔✔</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Start Designing Smarter Filtration Systems</h2>

  <div class="cta">
    <button class="primary">🚀 Launch Tool</button>
    <button class="secondary">📩 Contact Engineer</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
  Built by UNITE FILTER • Industrial Filtration Engineering Company
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
